1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection and tracking in images captured by drones. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper deals with drone-based platforms and their challenges. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper uses deep learning techniques for object detection and tracking. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses the RetinaNet model and SE blocks for improving performance. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with processing and analyzing images captured by drones.
